{"tid":408273,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛已經解決唔到既問題","createTime":"2017-09-21T05:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T08:14:00.000Z","uid":19863,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"190bb84b7571d0c04174f46309315654be4b124c","tid":408273,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"即使兩人或多或少仲有愛<br />\n但愛已經解決唔到互相之間積落既問題<br />\n而分手後 我仍然好愛佢<br />\n你地覺得仲有冇可能?<br />\n<br />\n正皮: 只要自己努力改變,佢個心一日有你就仲有機會<br />\n<br />\n負皮: 已經走到呢一步,愛已經包容唔落一切,可以嘗試但唔好太大期望<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我能力範圍內 唔犯法既任何事<br />\n我都會做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba09f4e5bf43238aef2146091bd88293d6ac175","tid":408273,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:01:21.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"9ea2efb4835813d3869541ca5a62288f70f2567c","tid":408273,"uid":42139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"冇，咪撚煩"},{"pid":"c429767acdd4368198da33641cff40200b842586","tid":408273,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"改變完即使佢唔會回頭 但你咪當令自己更好<br />\n每個人嘅改變唔係為人 係為自己㗎"},{"pid":"2bdfa410d81509079e8cd16fabf10a775cf51407","tid":408273,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇，咪撚煩</blockquote><br />\n明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0afe1050c86cb2bcaac36757e6bc8edcddad79","tid":408273,"uid":19863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>改變完即使佢唔會回頭 但你咪當令自己更好<br />\n每個人嘅改變唔係為人 係為自己㗎</blockquote><br />\n我知道 改變係為自己而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打"},{"pid":"895bdbe55bb2fb62302ef0c313a5f097a3859227","tid":408273,"uid":110075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:06:58.000Z","msg":"以前都覺只要2個人愛對方就所有野都解決到<br />\n但大大下先發覺原來愛真係唔係大晒<b