為左佢都一樣<br />\n我都真係必須要改變<br />\n改變係一世, 我都已經認定佢係我一世了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好羨慕你有呢種決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢會知你心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行動先係最實際<br />\n每推十次先行一步既我<br />\n都為自己今日許下嘅承諾<br />\n去奮鬥一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都希望佢心入面 仲有我<br />\n仲未去刪曬所有既回憶<br />\n仲留低我同佢之間每一個地方既腳印<br />\n我想返黎捉緊你 但依加既我未有能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecad52a047a983850bf20b58ee0d01340524ff7","tid":408273,"uid":19863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>解決唔到即是無愛</blockquote><br />\n係我付出太少 我認"}]}